# Personal IDE/agent settings
.claude/
.cursor/
.idea/
.vscode/

# Stray/empty
deploy/

# SSD staging output. stage-ssd.sh and stage-ssd-delta.sh write image
# tarballs (~6 GB each) plus rangerdanger.tgz; if the operator passes
# a relative output path like ./out instead of /Volumes/SOMETHING,
# the bundle lands inside the repo and would otherwise appear as
# untracked. External mounts (/Volumes/*) are already outside the
# working tree and not git's concern.
out/
images-amd64.tar
images-arm64.tar
delta-amd64.tar
delta-arm64.tar
rangerdanger.tgz
DELTA-README.md

# Large binary tools (not in git, fetched separately)
tools/pcap-analyzer/*.deb

# Local-only AI agent context (Claude Code)
CLAUDE.md

# Working backlog - kept local, not part of the public docs. ROADMAP.md
# is the public forward-looking doc; CHANGELOG.md is the public history.
# docs/tasks.md is private operator notes that aren't useful to external
# readers.
docs/tasks.md
